{
  "texts": [
    "The WikiQA dataset explores models for opendomain Q&A.",
    "The origin of questions is sourced from Bing query logs, and answers are derived from the content available on Wikipedia.",
    "A collective total of 3,047 questions has been gathered through crowdsourcing.",
    "• COPA (Roemmele et al, 2011).",
    "The COPA dataset is explicitly crafted for the common-sense causal reasoning task."
  ]
}